      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: May 10, 2026</p>
      <p>BondSBA Terminal provides SBA, bond, and business financing workflow tools for brokers, CPAs, surety teams, lenders, and financing partners.</p>
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect account information, authentication identifiers, uploaded or entered underwriting data, analysis inputs, generated outputs, and operational logs needed to provide and secure the service.</p>
      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>We use information to authenticate users, run requested analyses, store user-owned records, protect the platform, troubleshoot issues, and improve product reliability.</p>
      <h2>Service Providers</h2>
      <p>We use Supabase for authentication and database services, Vercel for hosting, Cloudflare Turnstile for bot protection, AI providers for analysis features requested by signed-in users, and Google AdSense for advertising when a visitor allows advertising cookies.</p>
      <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>Authentication cookies and local storage are used to keep users signed in. Advertising scripts are loaded only after a visitor chooses to allow ads in the consent banner. Visitors may reject advertising cookies and continue using the service.</p>
      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>BondSBA Terminal may display Google AdSense placements to keep the tools free. Google may process device, browser, and interaction information according to its own policies when advertising cookies are allowed.</p>
      <h2>Data Requests</h2>
      <p>To request access, correction, export, or deletion of your data, contact contactbondsba@gmail.com.</p>
      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>We use access controls, encrypted provider infrastructure, and authenticated API requests to protect user data. No online service can guarantee absolute security.</p>
